<XMLDocContent PageName="cobalt.graphics.IDataArrayOutput.Delete" Title="Delete method" xmlns="http://www.cobaltrenderer.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Paragraph>
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.Welcome">Home</PageRef> ->
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IDataArrayOutput">IDataArrayOutput</PageRef> ->
    Delete
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>Delete</TypeRef> method schedules the object for deletion. After calling this method, the object will be destroyed after the current frame completes drawing.
    </Paragraph>
    <Note Type="Important">
      <Paragraph>
        Objects created by an <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IRenderer">IRenderer</PageRef> use deferred deletion and remain alive until any frame that is already drawing no longer needs them.
      </Paragraph>
    </Note>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[void Delete();]]></Code>
  </Section>
